# {{intransitive}} To do a specific [[task]] by [[employ]]ing [[physical]] or [[mental]] [[power]]s.
#: ''He's working in a bar.''
# {{transitive}} To [[effect]] by [[gradual]] [[degree]]s.
#:''He '''worked''' his way through the crowd.''
